# Git Day 2

## What is git clone?

git clone creates a local copy of a remote repository.

## What is git pull?

git pull downloads and merges changes from GitHub.

## What is git fetch?

git fetch downloads changes without merging them.

## Difference Between Pull and Fetch

git fetch -> Download only

git pull -> Download + Merge

## Commands Learned

git clone
git pull
git fetch
git remote -v
git branch

## Key Takeaway

Clone copies a repository.
Pull syncs and updates it.
Fetch downloads updates safely.
